ass=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">A WORLD OF STRATEGY AWAITS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/3d468a58577143e9b0e9b3342437bac9.poster.avif?t=1774362361\" aria-label=\"Scenario from the game about the siege of a city done by a dragon, with units defending the settlement.\" width=616 height=410 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/3d468a58577143e9b0e9b3342437bac9.webm?t=1774362361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3119430/extras/3d468a58577143e9b0e9b3342437bac9.mp4?t=1774362361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legendary battles, emergent narrative and endless exploration - build your own grandeur in an accessible entry to the turn-based strategy games. Do you have what it takes to ascend?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
